query:
SELECT 
  qp.questionId,
  qp.firstAttemptStatus,
  qp.attemptCount,
  q.questionText
FROM question_progress qp
JOIN questions q ON qp.questionId = q.id
JOIN users u ON qp.userId = u.id
WHERE u.email = 'testyou@me.com'
  AND q.courseId = 2
  AND qp.firstAttemptStatus = 'incorrect';
